Mohamed Lamine Alhousseini Alhassan (amụrụ ya na Julaị 22, 1978) bụ onye Nijeria na-egwu egwuregwu mmiri. O sonyere na Summer Olympics nke afọ 2008na Men's 50m Freestyle event. O tinyere nọmba 4 na okpomọkụ nke abụọ nke agba nke mbụ na oge nke 30.90 sekọnd ma tinye onye nke iri itoolu na ise n'ozuzu.
